<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Wanderlust</title>
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

    <style>
        html,
        body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: black;
            font-family: 'Roboto', 'sans-serif';
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .logo {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1%;
            left: 2%;
            z-index: 5;
        }


        .title-and-pay-off {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: white;
        }

        .title {
            font-family: ;
        }

        .insta-logo {
            position: absolute;
            width: 220px;
            height: 220px;
            top: 20%;
            right: 10%;
        }

        .pin-picture {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: -2%;
            left: 50%;
            z-index: 5;
        }

        .floating-panel-center {
            position: fixed;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            top: 22%;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 40%;
            height: 40%;
            min-width: 300px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            z-index: 5;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            padding: 1%;
            border: 1px solid rgb(233, 231, 231);
            border-radius: 7px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1vw;
            line-height: 3vh;
            color: black;
        }

        .floating-panel-center button {
            background-color: green;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 32px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .floating-panel-center button:hover {
            background-color: darkgreen;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .map-picture {
            position: relative;
            left: 15%;
            right: 0%;
            top: 40%;
            bottom: 0;
            margin: 0 auto;
            z-index: 0;
            transform: rotate(-16deg);
        }

        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0%;
            left: 1%;
            right: 0%;
            z-index: 4;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1vw;
            color: white;
            line-height: 1vw;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="logo"><img src="public/images/logo.png" height="152" width="125"></div>

    <div class="title-and-pay-off">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>W A N D E R L U S T</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="pay-off">
            <h2>"not all those who wander are lost"</h2>
            <p><i>-- J.R.R. Tolkien</i></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="insta-logo"><img src="public/images/insta-logo.png" height="250" width="250"></div>
    <div class="pin-picture"><img src="public/images/pin-picture.png"></div>
    <div class="floating-panel-center">
        <h2>Welcome to Wanderlust!</h2>

        <h3>THE app that enables you to showcase your personal travel exploits on an interactive world map! It's plug 'n play! </h3>
        <h3>1. Just log in using your Instagram account and your geotagged photos will show automatically up on the map!</h3>
        <h3>2. Enjoy your personalized travel map, take a screenshot and share it with your friends!
        </h3>
        <a href="/authorize"><button>Click here to log in via Instagram</button></a>
    </div>
    <div class="map-picture"><img src="public/images/map-picture.png"></div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p><b>Â© Wanderlust 2019</b></p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
